name: You, me and festive dreams 🎄
description:
You, me and festive dreams 🎄

A special holiday season gift made in collaboration with dreamweaver.tez.

This image was generated by artificial intelligence generative adversarial network (VQGANCLIP). Keywords were used to guide the image. Animations and soundscapes were then added.

Im glad this image made it to you. I hope it brings a smile as an example of how simple images can propagate sprigs of joy.

For anyone who received this as their first ever NFT. Welcome!

Thanks for the support, ideas and encouragement Rich!

Happy holidays. 🎄🎁🎉

@i___am___yume. | iamyume.tez
